{"title":"Vue如何设置动态宽度高度或者动态样式","slug":"170","date":"2021-11-20T13:16:22.000Z","updated":"2021-11-20T13:31:14.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/170.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<p><strong>那么首先你务必看Vue的官方文档</strong>。涉及到的基础知识有：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=ywh5ME+vr94zX0POYV5pzA==.LkPk/572KTiXxePy+8Vd+YLGzDI3n7tMziUtx3qfLbIM2rdUYTj7pRppzF1UIxCNtFYq+sNnQm5PR46JR1syUzqbXxzdwkIirVJnd+7l6mTkKt/WuoAoHuHY+yVHITiwB9R9btzNhDsBNLJZg7kY3A==\">绑定内联样式的使用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=eA6DmzaSL7CrXc9GA5f2dA==.zuWJ9colkw967xDQDwTWMD4D668vG9h7ydjGDq8XNySyHVr9KNG+xo4WhN8skD4h\">computed的使用</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"1-添加样式绑定\"><a href=\"#1-添加样式绑定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 添加样式绑定\"></a>1. 添加样式绑定</h2><p>绑定高试样式</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;container&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">:style</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;&#123;height: scrollerHeight&#125;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-添加属性计算\"><a href=\"#2-添加属性计算\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 添加属性计算\"></a>2. 添加属性计算</h2><p>在<code>computed</code>里添加属性计算。记住 <code>scrollerHeight</code> 不能在<code>data</code>进行定义。<br><code>computed</code>是啥？请看看 <a href=\"https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=rTeX+W4eyebmFlKFLQ/NtQ==.KAWzo51JRIpUipEtZSO24Gy9/xIWPzDxfuBKunV7gTHiuivipVUep3iY0GsIf3Af\">computed的使用</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">computed: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 滚动区高度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// (业务需求：手机屏幕高度减去头部标题和底部tabbar的高度，当然这2个高度也是可以动态获取的)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">scrollerHeight</span>: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">window</span>.innerHeight - <span class=\"number\">40</span> - <span class=\"number\">54</span>) + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;px&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","more":"<p><strong>那么首先你务必看Vue的官方文档</strong>。涉及到的基础知识有：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=ywh5ME+vr94zX0POYV5pzA==.LkPk/572KTiXxePy+8Vd+YLGzDI3n7tMziUtx3qfLbIM2rdUYTj7pRppzF1UIxCNtFYq+sNnQm5PR46JR1syUzqbXxzdwkIirVJnd+7l6mTkKt/WuoAoHuHY+yVHITiwB9R9btzNhDsBNLJZg7kY3A==\">绑定内联样式的使用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=eA6DmzaSL7CrXc9GA5f2dA==.zuWJ9colkw967xDQDwTWMD4D668vG9h7ydjGDq8XNySyHVr9KNG+xo4WhN8skD4h\">computed的使用</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"1-添加样式绑定\"><a href=\"#1-添加样式绑定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 添加样式绑定\"></a>1. 添加样式绑定</h2><p>绑定高试样式</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;container&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">:style</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;&#123;height: scrollerHeight&#125;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-添加属性计算\"><a href=\"#2-添加属性计算\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 添加属性计算\"></a>2. 添加属性计算</h2><p>在<code>computed</code>里添加属性计算。记住 <code>scrollerHeight</code> 不能在<code>data</code>进行定义。<br><code>computed</code>是啥？请看看 <a href=\"https://link.segmentfault.com/?enc=rTeX+W4eyebmFlKFLQ/NtQ==.KAWzo51JRIpUipEtZSO24Gy9/xIWPzDxfuBKunV7gTHiuivipVUep3iY0GsIf3Af\">computed的使用</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">computed: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 滚动区高度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// (业务需求：手机屏幕高度减去头部标题和底部tabbar的高度，当然这2个高度也是可以动态获取的)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">scrollerHeight</span>: <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">window</span>.innerHeight - <span class=\"number\">40</span> - <span class=\"number\">54</span>) + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;px&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":[{"name":"uni-app开发","path":"api/categories/uni-app开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"微信小程序","path":"api/tags/微信小程序.json"},{"name":"Vue","path":"api/tags/Vue.json"},{"name":"uni-app开发","path":"api/tags/uni-app开发.json"}]}